{"tid":2392663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登簽行政命令　無證移民家庭可團聚","createTime":"2021-02-03T02:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T04:06:24.000Z","uid":318316,"like":13,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"87e08cae8ce6ed7daf8e354d4c25b8ec2a3fa0f2","tid":2392663,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登簽署了三項行政命令，推翻特朗普政令，令無證移民家庭得以團聚；又要求政府重新審視移民措施。<br />\n共和黨的前總統特朗普為阻移民流入，要求跨越美墨邊境的無證移民，把未成年人士和成年家人分開安置，至少5500名兒童受影響，遭人權組織嚴厲批評。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-03-2021/70134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F02-03-2021%2F70134&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=c4bbbacd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-03-2021/70134</a>"},{"pid":"561449abe8aae7fa400fe7675b59c467e1e7097b","tid":2392663,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912f96da5a962077046333cc2cf829240564d2be","tid":2392663,"uid":5945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"攞和平獎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bce55b668393656aca73bd2ecd1c2d7b22d3935","tid":2392663,"uid":208323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"熱血時報批評特朗普？<br />\n明明係奧巴馬政策（好似係）"},{"pid":"0d3b65709e76c54760c768a4b8ee5a94d491da61","tid":2392663,"uid":56428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"香港都要團聚了"},{"pid":"6fa4a7465db38fca886e914cd6df3677df76c2df","tid":2392663,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"港